data.description: Welcome to this beautiful 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom and 2 car garage, move in ready home. With a beautiful curb appeal, with a front porch. Walking into the house, you see a lovely fireplace ready for those cooler evenings and a huge living room. To the right side you see the kitchen, with stainless steal appliances, granite counter tops, ceramic tile backsplash. HVAC: 2019. There is a big enclosed backyard.
